{"tid":1133591,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"<逃犯條例> 其實香港人喺世界任何地方都可以觸犯大陸法律","createTime":"2019-05-01T07:37:39.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-13T15:54:50.000Z","uid":31208,"like":32,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"c7f6177bebe0885e10171a544f2f3dc7618985d9","tid":1133591,"uid":31208,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-01T07:37:39.000Z","msg":"簡體字預警<br />\n<br />\n中華人民共和國&lt;刑法&gt;<br />\n<br />\n第七条    中华人民共和国公民在中华人民共和国领域外犯本法规定之罪的，适用本法，但是按本法规定的最高刑为三年以下有期徒刑的，可以不予追究。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n香港人係共產黨眼中就係中華人民共和國公民，鬧佢幾句已經可以當你顛覆國家政權，拉你移交番大陸受審。<br />\n<br />\n仲勁過23條，將來犯23條都係坐赤柱監獄啫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a8ce8eb777f12c7184a1d2ed3f2da163dc69e4c5","tid":1133591,"uid":55597,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-01T07:39:44.000Z","msg":"基本上去中國敵對國，已經可以屈你賣國"},{"pid":"2146816fc8d6f512c36a2b377904a729e699b8d3","tid":1133591,"uid":6752,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-01T07:40:53.000Z","msg":"咪光明正大要你交人,咩國家都唔關事<br />\n正式同支那接軌"},{"pid":"312547375d5eeae0022462389a41c21b142ee3ff","tid":1133591,"uid":4574,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-01T08:11:32.000Z","msg":"是旦鋤你一條罪<br />\n好似美國佬屈阿桑奇老強"},{"pid":"4bcca1d5c2aa0b3df3a40f750aae54590a2cba45","tid":1133591,"uid":54884,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-01T08:30:47.000Z","msg":"都話要香港都係犯法先得"},{"pid":"8e699e8b6aac2051f4e9e7d2a597fc52b2316ba1","tid":1133591,"uid":5627,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-04T04:56:28.000Z","msg":"Pish"},{"pid":"657ba4130d72ba8cfaa4d519564447fa03651fc9","tid":1133591,"uid":5627,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-04T08:44:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"035